  <div class="scrolling-section">
    <div id="about-me">
      <h2 id="about-me-header">ABOUT ME</h2>
      <div>
        <p>
          I am an undergraduate software engineer studying at McGill University, Canada.
          My passions are in low level software development, cybersecurity and game development.
